<HEADLINE> Stock Prices Fall in London / British Stocks  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LONDON (AP) -- Share prices were marginally lower on the London  
Stock Exchange on Thursday. 
</P>
<P>
	The Financial Times Stock Exchange 100-share index fell 3.9  
points, or 0.1 percent, to 5,872.5. 
</P>
<P>
	Provisional volume was 1.20 billion shares, compared with 1.20  
billion on Wednesday. 
</P>
</TEXT>
