<HEADLINE> Bucks Acquire Vinny Del Negro </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	MILWAUKEE (AP) -- Vinny Del Negro agreed in principle Thursday to  
a contract with the Milwaukee Bucks after six seasons with the San 
Antonio Spurs. 
</P>
<P>
	Del Negro, a shooting guard, averaged 9.5 points and 3.4 assists  
in 54 games last season. In his eight-year NBA career, Del Negro 
has averaged 10.4 points and 3.4 assists. 
</P>
<P>
	Del Negro, who played two seasons in Italy before joining the  
Spurs in 1992-93, had been playing in Italy during the NBA lockout. 
</P>
<P>
