his sentence was read and was not surprised by the outcome. 
</P>
<P>
	``He's extremely remorseful,'' Welch said.  
</P>
<P>
	Herek and church officials still face a civil lawsuit filed in  
September on behalf of the altar boy. It accuses the Omaha 
Archdiocese of negligence. 
