<HEADLINE> Big Movers in the Stock Market  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Stocks that are moving substantially or trading  
heavily today on the New York Stock Exchange, Nasdaq Stock Market, 
and American Stock Exchange. 

</P>
<P>
                               *NYSE    	

</P>
<P>
 *Lucent Technologies Inc., up 3 1/16 at 114 9/16.    	
</P>
<P>
	The technology company formed a new division to focus on the  
growing market for speech products in communications networks, 
including speech-recognition technology that can turn recorded 
spoken words into text. 

</P>
<P>
 *Alcatel, down 15/16 at 22 3/8.    	
</P>
<P>
	The French telecommunications equipment supplier released  
disappointing earnings results. 

</P>
<P>
